{"prompt": "Design a corporate site for a document management system. The design should be organized and use a crisp yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureDocs - Document Management System</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFDA62; /* Crisp yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #FDF4C3; /* Lighter yellow */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --dark-text-color: #000000;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureDocs</h1>\n        <p>Your Ultimate Document Management Solution</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Organize. Secure. Access.</h2>\n        <p>Streamline your workflow with a powerful, intuitive, and secure document management system designed for modern businesses.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Why Choose SecureDocs?</h2>\n            <p>In today's fast-paced business environment, efficient document management is crucial. SecureDocs provides a centralized, secure, and accessible platform for all your important files.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Key Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#9728;</span> Robust Security</h3>\n                    <p>State-of-the-art encryption and access controls to protect your sensitive data.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#128213;</span> Version Control</h3>\n                    <p>Track changes, revert to previous versions, and maintain a clear history of your documents.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#128205;</span> Collaboration Tools</h3>\n                    <p>Easily share, comment, and co-edit documents with your team in real-time.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#128395;</span> Advanced Search</h3>\n                    <p>Find any document instantly with powerful search capabilities, including full-text search.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#128193;</span> Audit Trails</h3>\n                    <p>Maintain compliance with detailed logs of all document activity.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3><span style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">&#127760;</span> Scalability</h3>\n                    <p>Grows with your business, handling any volume of documents.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\" id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your Document Management?</h2>\n            <p>Contact us today for a personalized demo and see how SecureDocs can benefit your organization.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@securedocs.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Sales</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureDocs. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}